<template>
  <button @click="fetchData">Clicca</button>
  
</template>

<script>
import axios from "axios";
import {toRaw} from "vue";

export default {
  name: "AgendaPage",
  data(){
    return{
      state : 1
    }
  },
  methods : {
    async fetchData(){
      try {
        const response = await axios.get('ServletGetBookingsForUser',{params : {action : 'web',stato : toRaw(this.state)}})
        console.log(response.data);
      }catch (e){
        console.error(e);
      }
    }
  }
}
</script>
